<br />\nAsso仔只係DSE考得差, 唔代表D咩<br />\nHKU都好多讀死書的腦殘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Asso 仔唔差，佢地 gpa 閒閒地都高過唔少大學生"},{"pid":"a563dbac7a01b3f0f3f74d824c599ced410f60ee","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人明讀書唔掂有幾慘"},{"pid":"b9cd0f9d420af504ee3146ac0c48505d7deaae10","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:14:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5ac64be6756f9109e4531b6a28988260b4778c2","tid":339173,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你語文差D定數學差D?</blockquote><br />\n語文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係數學唔差la!<br />\n<br />\n你打機叻唔叻?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓豬數學5**</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成全呀，5**唔代表讀得掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係代表有努力過</blockquote><br />\n你叫冇5**既情何以堪"},{"pid":"95e852103cdb3fd37bb92301c9c4b06e14d22fde","tid":339173,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬小心比嗰班真正讀書唔成 要靠走後門先入到u嘅asshole仔咬</blockquote><br />\n讀 Asso 唔代表讀書唔成，好可能只係一時失手，你可以問下佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果asso仔無失手嘅話 <br />\ndse會唔會有廿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd84a2b78de29d02f3c5e57bad741a1681079aa","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a434a439cd9616dc85dacf694964720e6faf54f2","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀書要考試要交功課要上堂，好討厭呢種學習模式</blockquote><br />\n有無報考 CFA?</blockquote><br />\n已經plan 咗幾時報，不過考完都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29af74356bb7eabf66be2568b7a7e76a79f392fd","tid":339173,"uid":113868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家做緊嘢定讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊咩<br />\n咩科<br />\n打算做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊 HKU, EnF<br />\n唔知做咩，想做關於 Finance 方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfinancial planner算唔算做金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算，係專業人士，話曬都要考牌<br />\n其實我覺得有啲Asso仔仲叻過我大學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso仔只係DSE考得差, 唔代表D咩<br />\nHKU都好多讀死書的腦殘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Asso 仔唔差，佢地 gpa 閒閒地都高過唔少大學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到你25歲時, 你會發現無人會理你有幾多個5**, 無人理你有無船, 無人理你GPA幾多。<br />\n<br />\n就好似你小學年年拎第一, 你會唔會攞出黎講?"},{"pid":"2a22d93069ab12c1015fc19971e0dddb897c4ded","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你語文差D定數學差D?</blockquote><br />\n語文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係數學唔差la!<br />\n<br />\n你打機叻唔叻?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓豬數學5**</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成全呀，5**唔代表讀得掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係代表有努力過</blockquote><br />\n你叫冇5**既情何以堪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係佢地未發力"},{"pid":"3981c16590c707ea3859e543c96ad76f0b6f9894","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:17:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b5e39c549cb94d5752cf5eb366e949043a02897","tid":339173,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家做緊嘢定讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊咩<br />\n咩科<br />\n打算做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊 HKU, EnF<br />\n唔知做咩，想做關於 Finance 方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfinancial planner算唔算做金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算，係專業人士，話曬都要考牌<br />\n其實我覺得有啲Asso仔仲叻過我大學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso仔只係DSE考得差, 唔代表D咩<br />\nHKU都好多讀死書的腦殘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Asso 仔唔差，佢地 gpa 閒閒地都高過唔少大學生</blockquote><br />\n好多大學生入到u就掛住玩<br />\n完全唔讀書<br />\n先搞到低gpa<br />\n如果佢哋肯乖乖哋去讀書 根本無可能廢過asso仔"},{"pid":"805a6c1a3ed746456e1f6789cd8aa406345eb1eb","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aeee803d5c9c34954e3280c77c53f53cfc8d4ae","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬小心比嗰班真正讀書唔成 要靠走後門先入到u嘅asshole仔咬</blockquote><br />\n讀 Asso 唔代表讀書唔成，好可能只係一時失手，你可以問下佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果asso仔無失手嘅話 <br />\ndse會唔會有廿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常溫下書25分以上好多人都得<br />\nAsso 仔唔會失手，因為知道自己失手會retake 唔係去讀 Asso"},{"pid":"a267063f4de557d03d232a8a6e91cd01ef0b5d33","tid":339173,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家做緊嘢定讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊咩<br />\n咩科<br />\n打算做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊 HKU, EnF<br />\n唔知做咩，想做關於 Finance 方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfinancial planner算唔算做金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算，係專業人士，話曬都要考牌<br />\n其實我覺得有啲Asso仔仲叻過我大學生</blockquote><br />\n有牌就專業嘅話 咁即係保安都係專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實保安牌定保險牌難考啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保安牌難啲，冇乜大學生考，代表唔係讀書叻就有</blockquote><br />\n保安有撚難考咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文都唔駛識坐兩日考 QAS 再交低幾舊水就可以等拎SPP開工</blockquote><br />\nWait 2 weeks<br />\nGet 2 referees<br />\nThen have work</blockquote><br />\n其實保險牌都係咁上下"},{"pid":"5430eb2e270174ccbe44745fdab32f48e7a1d584","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"092614d7d6d8fa07972031cf2b2db99d7ff10295","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家做緊嘢定讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊咩<br />\n咩科<br />\n打算做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊 HKU, EnF<br />\n唔知做咩，想做關於 Finance 方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfinancial planner算唔算做金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算，係專業人士，話曬都要考牌<br />\n其實我覺得有啲Asso仔仲叻過我大學生</blockquote><br />\n有牌就專業嘅話 咁即係保安都係專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實保安牌定保險牌難考啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保安牌難啲，冇乜大學生考，代表唔係讀書叻就有</blockquote><br />\n保安有撚難考咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英文都唔駛識坐兩日考 QAS 再交低幾舊水就可以等拎SPP開工</blockquote><br />\nWait 2 weeks<br />\nGet 2 referees<br />\nThen have work</blockquote><br />\n仲有樓主要入 iBank 做 System Analyst 唔該報 Phy/Math/Stat Master</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時候去 food bank 唔好笑我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1a6dc1e1c70b98b7de1e1786b541b364f30f48","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬小心比嗰班真正讀書唔成 要靠走後門先入到u嘅asshole仔咬</blockquote><br />\n讀 Asso 唔代表讀書唔成，好可能只係一時失手，你可以問下佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果asso仔無失手嘅話 <br />\ndse會唔會有廿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常溫下書25分以上好多人都得<br />\nAsso 仔唔會失手，因為知道自己失手會retake 唔係去讀 Asso</blockquote><br />\n你小心D<br />\n00後好多都好勤力<br />\n就算自己夠醒目都唔好輕視佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n00後真係另一個世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35886cf7322fdb3a35a9ba497d9fc2ac90df8068","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:22:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2287d9b1e1aef70e8089f8896cff7ebe694100c9","tid":339173,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬小心比嗰班真正讀書唔成 要靠走後門先入到u嘅asshole仔咬</blockquote><br />\n讀 Asso 唔代表讀書唔成，好可能只係一時失手，你可以問下佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果asso仔無失手嘅話 <br />\ndse會唔會有廿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常溫下書25分以上好多人都得<br />\nAsso 仔唔會失手，因為知道自己失手會retake 唔係去讀 Asso</blockquote><br />\n樓豬講出咗重點啦<br />\n班asso仔根本就唔係因為失手先低分<br />\n低分只係佢哋實力嘅反映<br />\n但偏偏班asso仔最鍾意賴失手"},{"pid":"ac4a5dbaa9966f7e2db7e812221797d5630f7b95","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家做緊嘢定讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊咩<br />\n咩科<br />\n打算做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊 HKU, EnF<br />\n唔知做咩，想做關於 Finance 方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfinancial planner算唔算做金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算，係專業人士，話曬都要考牌<br />\n其實我覺得有啲Asso仔仲叻過我大學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso仔只係DSE考得差, 唔代表D咩<br />\nHKU都好多讀死書的腦殘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Asso 仔唔差，佢地 gpa 閒閒地都高過唔少大學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到你25歲時, 你會發現無人會理你有幾多個5**, 無人理你有無船, 無人理你GPA幾多。<br />\n<br />\n就好似你小學年年拎第一, 你會唔會攞出黎講?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打鼓勵"},{"pid":"553858f231c7da1d8addb0bb4a98f3ec96a31cdc","tid":339173,"uid":113868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家做緊嘢定讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊書</blockquote><br />\n讀緊咩<br />\n咩科<br />\n打算做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊 HKU, EnF<br />\n唔知做咩，想做關於 Finance 方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfinancial planner算唔算做金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算，係專業人士，話曬都要考牌<br />\n其實我覺得有啲Asso仔仲叻過我大學生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso仔只係DSE考得差, 唔代表D咩<br />\nHKU都好多讀死書的腦殘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Asso 仔唔差，佢地 gpa 閒閒地都高過唔少大學生</blockquote><br />\n好多大學生入到u就掛住玩<br />\n完全唔讀書<br />\n先搞到低gpa<br />\n如果佢哋肯乖乖哋去讀書 根本無可能廢過asso仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實Asso升左degree, 就係degree la, 點解要分佢地曾經係asso呢"},{"pid":"fc1e31aae6b22fef94b180d420d87201f02ead20","tid":339173,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21f9cfc63dcdf0415fe880e121346f7fd5f7d012","tid":339173,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T22:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquot